overview:
Industry Vantage provides trade associations and industry groups with online industry marketplaces, industry e-newsletters, ad & media publishing and non-dues revenue.

Associations can keep their brand top of mind with their members and attract prospective members by offering Industry Vantage’s highly-relevant and proprietary publications which create high engagement, retention and revenue.

As of late 2012, Industry Vantage publishes into 6 industries with one or more sites per industry.

Example industry sites include: http://www.SnackFoodIndustryMarketplace.com http://www.BakingIndustryBuyersGuide.com http://www.PackagingIndustryMarketplace.com http://www.WasteandRecyclingMarketplace.com
